                            </span>
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu animation-dock">
                            <li class="dropdown-header">Configuração</li>
                            <li>
                                <a href="#">Perfil</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="divider"></li>
                            <li>
